title: E133 COUNTDOWN TO FIGHT NIGHT WITH LOGAN PAUL - IMPAULSIVE EP. 133

description:
In this final episode before the fight, Logan and Mike reminisce about their vanishing sex life, being absent from LA Halloween parties, and a $30,000 bet placed on Logan. Also... IMPAULSIVE is NOT the number one podcast in the world? Logan is going to fight a Sirius XM Radio Host? Mike is actually a good guy?
